title: Black N Brew
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house also serving food, including vegan treats and vegan soups. Has tofu and seitan dishes, veggie sausage, vegan cream cheese, and soy milk for drinks. Free internet access and supports local artists. Confirmed open Nov. 2013.
